OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK should update the price cap on  
OL,6, energy bills every three months instead
OL,7, of twice a year to help households, the
OL,8, energy watchdog has proposed.          
OL,10,FOfgem said that a more frequent price  
OL,11,Fcap would reflect the most up-to-date  
OL,12,Fenergy prices.                         
OL,14,FIt would mean "when prices fall from   
OL,15,Fthe current record highs, customers    
OL,16,Fwould see the benefit much sooner".    
OL,18,FHouseholds are already facing pressure 
OL,19,Ffrom high gas and electricity prices   
OL,20,Fafter the price cap rose in April.     
